name: AFRICAN Beauty Butter- Intensive Dry Skin Treatment
size1: Scent: Ugandan Vanilla and Ethiopian Honey
ingredients: -Shea Butter: Intensely rich, creamy moisturizer, excellent for dry, cracked skin. -Baobab Oil: Excellent for softening skin and maintaining a healthy skin barrier. -Jojoba Oil: Lightweight, vitamin-rich, penetrates deep to nourish and protect skin.
